      "text": [
        "3961 - وَ قَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"اَلْجَالِبُ مَرْزُوقٌ وَ اَلْمُحْتَكِرُ مَلْعُونٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3961 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace be upon him and his family, said:\n\"The one who brings goods to the market is blessed with sustenance, and the hoarder is cursed.\""
        ]
      }
